bullets:

aplus_text: The Solimo premium 144 TC bedsheet range is made from 100% cotton. This  double bedsheet is made from cotton that has been combed to retain only  long cotton fibers. This process makes the yarn strong and soft making  the bedsheet long lasting and soft to touch. The cotton fibers drain  away moisture, making the bedsheet breathable and comfortable.This bedsheet is suitable for use all-year round because cotton as a  fabric keeps you cool during summers and warm during winters.Please Note: Image is for illustration purpose only.When buying a bedsheet you should check for TC or thread count which refers to the number of threads that make up one square inch of fabric. Typically, the finer the threads that can be woven together, the softer the fabric. The Solimo premium range of double bedsheets with 144 TC are soft, comfortable and suitable for all seasons. Each Solimo bedsheet is crafted to be light-weight and easy to wash at home.Solimo printed double bedsheets come in a large size: 90 inch x 100 inch or 228 cm x 254 cm, for making it easy to tuck-in below the bed. It is ideal for use on double beds with size 5 ft x 6.25 ft or smaller.You can use Solimo bedsheets all through the year. With a wide range of colours, designs and patterns, we help you create a unique look for your home. You can choose from amongst different designs such as floral, abstract and geometric to find a set that best suits your tastes and existing home decor.Welcome to the world of Solimo - a place where premium quality and great value go hand in hand. Every Solimo product is carefully built to deliver exceptional quality. Right from the materials used, to detailed quality checks, to thoughtful improvements, quality is at the core of everything we do. We invest our resources only on what is important to you and minimize costs on things like packaging, advertising and other extras that don’t add value. This helps us keep our costs low and create products that deliver more value for the price you pay. Expect a little more every time you buy a Solimo product.

aplus_text: The Solimo premium 144 TC bedsheet range is made from 100% cotton. This  double bedsheet is made from cotton that has been combed to retain only  long cotton fibers. This process makes the yarn strong and soft making  the bedsheet long lasting and soft to touch. The cotton fibers drain  away moisture, making the bedsheet breathable and comfortable.This bedsheet is suitable for use all-year round because cotton as a  fabric keeps you cool during summers and warm during winters.Please Note: Image is for illustration purpose only.When buying a bedsheet you should check for TC or thread count which refers to the number of threads that make up one square inch of fabric. Typically, the finer the threads that can be woven together, the softer the fabric. The Solimo premium range of double bedsheets with 144 TC are soft, comfortable and suitable for all seasons. Each Solimo bedsheet is crafted to be light-weight and easy to wash at home.Solimo printed double bedsheets come in a large size: 90 inch x 100 inch or 228 cm x 254 cm, for making it easy to tuck-in below the bed. It is ideal for use on double beds with size 5 ft x 6.25 ft or smaller.You can use Solimo bedsheets all through the year. With a wide range of colours, designs and patterns, we help you create a unique look for your home. You can choose from amongst different designs such as floral, abstract and geometric to find a set that best suits your tastes and existing home decor.Welcome to the world of Solimo - a place where premium quality and great value go hand in hand. Every Solimo product is carefully built to deliver exceptional quality. Right from the materials used, to detailed quality checks, to thoughtful improvements, quality is at the core of everything we do. We invest our resources only on what is important to you and minimize costs on things like packaging, advertising and other extras that don’t add value. This helps us keep our costs low and create products that deliver more value for the price you pay. Expect a little more every time you buy a Solimo product.

The cotton  fibers drain  away moisture, making the bedsheet breathable and  comfortable.This bedsheet is suitable for use all-year round because  cotton as a  fabric keeps you cool during summers and warm during  winters.Please Note: Image is for illustration purpose only.When buying a bedsheet you should check for TC or thread  count which refers to the number of threads that make up one square inch  of fabric. Typically, the finer the threads that can be woven together,  the softer the fabric. The Solimo premium range of single bedsheets  with 144 TC are soft, comfortable and suitable for all seasons. Each  Solimo bedsheet is crafted to be light-weight and easy to wash at home.Solimo printed single bedsheets come in a large size: 60  inch x 90 inch or 152 cm x 228 cm, for making it easy to tuck-in below  the bed. It is ideal for use on single beds with size 3 ft x 6.25 ft or  smaller.You can use Solimo bedsheets all through the year. With a  wide range of colours, designs and patterns, we help you create a unique  look for your home. You can choose from amongst different designs such  as floral, abstract and geometric to find a set that best suits your  tastes and existing home decor.Welcome to the world of Solimo - a place where premium   quality and great value go hand in hand. Every Solimo product is   carefully built to deliver exceptional quality. Right from the materials   used, to detailed quality checks, to thoughtful improvements, quality   is at the core of everything we do.We invest our resources only on what is important to you and   minimize costs on things like packaging, advertising and other extras   that don’t add value. This helps us keep our costs low and create   products that deliver more value for the price you pay. Expect a little   more every time you buy a Solimo product.

Superior quality 100% combed cotton fibres helps reduce lint buildup & ensures durability of the towels keeping them fresh & bright for a longer period.Solimo towels are available in 5 specially processed fade resistant colors - Iris Blue, Spanish Red, and Paradise Pink to Sunshine Yellow and Spring Green. Choose from the different colour combination packs to find a set that best suits your taste and existing home décor.Welcome to the world of Solimo – a place where premium quality and great value go hand in hand. Every Solimo product is carefully built to deliver exceptional quality. Right from the materials used, to detailed quality checks, to thoughtful improvements, quality is at the core of everything we do. aplus_text: The Solimo premium 144 TC bedsheet range is made from 100% cotton. This  double bedsheet is made from cotton that has been combed to retain only  long cotton fibers. This process makes the yarn strong and soft making  the bedsheet long lasting and soft to touch. The cotton fibers drain  away moisture, making the bedsheet breathable and comfortable.This bedsheet is suitable for use all-year round because cotton as a  fabric keeps you cool during summers and warm during winters.Please Note: Image is for illustration purpose only.When buying a bedsheet you should check for TC or thread count which refers to the number of threads that make up one square inch of fabric. Typically, the finer the threads that can be woven together, the softer the fabric. The Solimo premium range of double bedsheets with 144 TC are soft, comfortable and suitable for all seasons. Each Solimo bedsheet is crafted to be light-weight and easy to wash at home.Solimo printed double bedsheets come in a large size: 90 inch x 100 inch or 228 cm x 254 cm, for making it easy to tuck-in below the bed. It is ideal for use on double beds with size 5 ft x 6.25 ft or smaller.You can use Solimo bedsheets all through the year. With a wide range of colours, designs and patterns, we help you create a unique look for your home. You can choose from amongst different designs such as floral, abstract and geometric to find a set that best suits your tastes and existing home decor.Welcome to the world of Solimo - a place where premium quality and great value go hand in hand. Every Solimo product is carefully built to deliver exceptional quality. Right from the materials used, to detailed quality checks, to thoughtful improvements, quality is at the core of everything we do. We invest our resources only on what is important to you and minimize costs on things like packaging, advertising and other extras that don’t add value. This helps us keep our costs low and create products that deliver more value for the price you pay. Expect a little more every time you buy a Solimo product.

aplus_text: For a coordinated, everyday ensemble, turn to this six-piece  cotton towel set by AmazonBasics. The plush towel set offers a lighter  weight, fluffy softness, and quick absorbency, which means ultimate  comfort and fast results when drying your hands and face after washing  up or drying off after stepping out of a hot shower.The towels can be machine washed then tossed in the dryer for easy care.Made from 100-percent cotton, the towels not only feels soft  to the touch and smooth against skin, but it also stands up over time,  offering tear-resistant strength and long-lasting durability.The fade-resistant color means that even after several  washings, the towels will continue to retain their handsome hue. Ideal  for the kid's bathroom, a guest bathroom, or even as a set when sending  the eldest off to college, the six-piece cotton towel set brings  affordable convenience to the daily routine. Whether hung together in  the bathroom or neatly folded and stacked in the closet, you can never  have too many towels.

aplus_text: Made from 380 GSM, 100% cotton, this bathrobe with strong fibers is soft, comfortable, highly absorbent and long-lasting. The inner and outer terrycloth fabric absorbs moisture and keeps you warm after a bath. Its velvet-like finish further enhances the aesthetic appeal and provides a luxurious experience.Available with two options. With a length of 122 cm and 107 cm, the bathrobe can be comfortably worn at home, by the swimming pool, beach or at the spa without the fear of exposure. This large-sized robe is suitable for people with height above 5’ 5’’.100% Cotton Unisex Bathrobe has two pockets on the front that allow you to carry your mobile, wallet, keys and other essentials, thus keeping your hands free. Sleek shawl collar enhances the coziness of the robe. It is equipped with an adjustable belt that allows you to wrap the robe tightly around your body. This belt is removable in case you don’t need it.You can wrap it around as lounge-wear in your leisure time at home or carry it to dry yourself after you hit the swimming pool or beach. Furthermore, this stylish robe can also be worn at a spa.
bullets:
Care Instructions: Machine Wash  
, Fit Type: Regular  
, Velour Bathrobe - Our luxurious Bathrobe is crafted from pure 100% finest quality soft cotton material with velvet like feel to ensure they have not only excellent absorbency properties but also manages to combine luxurious softness to skin with ultra lightweight quality. The robe features a shawl collar for extra warmth, 2 front pockets, wide cuffs and a matching belt.  
, Stylish Design - Style and design have always been our niche. With this we present you with an ultimate bathrobe to stay comfortable and still feel upscale. It also comes with a classic tailored fit along with two pockets and double cuffs. Not to forget, the robe has wrist length sleeves and a streamlined flat collar, which makes it easy to carry. The next time you visit a spa with your friends, do remember to flaunt the soft and plush collar and the matching belt of your new stylish robe.  
, Comfortable Size & Use - Our bathrobe is available in 2 standard sizes. One is suitable with Small-Medium-S/M size measures length 42" & Width 22". You can buy this bathrobe; if you fall in the S/M size category. The comfortable size gives you the space to enjoy your moment alone or with your friends. This robe feactures an adjustable outer belt tie for a perfect fit. Moreover, the super soft touch allows you to wear these bathrobes round the year.  
, Easy care - Our bathrobes are completely machine washable. You can dry but on low setting. It is very easy to maintain the quality of the bathrobe as it is made from pure cotton. You can wear it directly after drying it, there is no need to iron the bathrobe.  
, We Value You- We guarantee you the return acceptance of the product within 30 days of its purchase, without having the need to mention the reason for the same. Not to forget, the product should not be used by you. It should be sent back in the same condition, as handed over by our delivering partners.

bullets:
Super Premium Bedsheet Collection -Pamper yourself with our super soft and high-quality 100% cotton sheets that provide unparalleled softness, breathability, and durability. The ultimate retreat at the start and end of each day is like falling into soft, luxurious bed sheets and a fresh feel with waking up each morning. Our Classic Collection suits modern sensibilities with its classic appeal and rich color palette.  
, Bed Sheet Set - Classic collection king size premium bedsheet set includes 1 bedsheet - 274 cm x 274 cm or 108 inches x 108 inches and 2 pillow covers - 46 cm x 69 cm or 18 inches x 27 inches each.  
, Technology Meets Luxury - The Classic bedsheet set is designed with 100% cotton created by engaging our patented Air-Rich technology. Its distinct feel comes from the unique properties of Moisture Management Finish, which helps in wicking and temperature regulation. This sheet set is an OEKO-TEX certified skin-friendly product. This is an independent certification system that ensures that textiles meet high safety and environmental standards and are free from harmful chemicals.  
, Easy Care - For best use, wash separately on first use. Hand wash or machine wash warm. Do not use bleach. Line dry in the shade and wash dark colors separately. Iron on medium heat and do not dry clean.  
, We Value You - We do follow an excellent quality-making process that gives us 100% confidence in our products. We are here to provide satisfaction to our customers because we value you. Please feel free to reach out to us!

aplus_text: Made from 100% cotton , these sheets are super soft and durable.. It is available in variety of designs with two sizes Queen and Single. These sheets are Soft, lightweight, breathable and gentle perfect for your daily use. Our unique process enhances the softness of the sheets with each washing and bed sheets become even softer & cozier.Trident presents Simply Modern sheet sets which are made of 120 thread count. Nothing would better than a sound sleep, as we spend one-third of our life on the bed. So, experience your endless sleep time with our Simply Modern sheets which are made of 100% Cotton.We try to inch you closer to your 'dream home' with our thoughtful and colorful brands, woven with utmost love to soothe your soul and calm your senses. Crafted from the softest fibers, carefully hand-picked just for you, we weave magnificence into every thread. We have a vast range of products to suit every possible need.When it comes to aesthetics, superior quality and great value, our much-loved offerings are the perfect choice. We believe in making the simplest pleasure of life a luxurious one. Every article is crafted beautifully to add a contemporary as well as classical art of living to any home.You can handwash these cotton sheets and dry in shade. Also, washing with machine is a suitable option, but with luke warm water to reduce wrinkles. It can be tumble dry on low heat. It is recommended to not bleach and dry clean the product. Further, remember to wash the dark colors separately.

aplus_text: The Solimo premium 144 TC bedsheet range is made from 100% cotton. This double bedsheet is made from cotton that has been combed to retain only long cotton fibers. This process makes the yarn strong and soft making the bedsheet long lasting and soft to touch. The cotton fibers drain away moisture, making the bedsheet breathable and comfortable.This bedsheet is suitable for use all-year round because cotton as a fabric keeps you cool during summers and warm during winters.Please Note: Image is for illustration purpose only.When buying a bedsheet you should check for TC or thread count which refers to the number of threads that make up one square inch of fabric. Typically, the finer the threads that can be woven together, the softer the fabric. The Solimo premium range of double bedsheets with 144 TC are soft, comfortable and suitable for all seasons. Each Solimo bedsheet is crafted to be light-weight and easy to wash at home.Solimo printed double bedsheets come in a large size: 90 inch x 100 inch or 228 cm x 254 cm, for making it easy to tuck-in below the bed. It is ideal for use on double beds with size 5 ft x 6.25 ft or smaller.You can use Solimo bedsheets all through the year. With a wide range of colours, designs and patterns, we help you create a unique look for your home. You can choose from amongst different designs such as floral, abstract and geometric to find a set that best suits your tastes and existing home decor.Welcome to the world of Solimo - a place where premium quality and great value go hand in hand. Every Solimo product is carefully built to deliver exceptional quality. Right from the materials used, to detailed quality checks, to thoughtful improvements, quality is at the core of everything we do. We invest our resources only on what is important to you and minimize costs on things like packaging, advertising and other extras that don’t add value. This helps us keep our costs low and create products that deliver more value for the price you pay. Expect a little more every time you buy a Solimo product.

aplus_text: The Solimo premium 144 TC bedsheet range is made from 100% cotton. This double bedsheet is made from cotton that has been combed to retain only long cotton fibers. This process makes the yarn strong and soft making the bedsheet long lasting and soft to touch. The cotton fibers drain away moisture, making the bedsheet breathable and comfortable.This bedsheet is suitable for use all-year round because cotton as a fabric keeps you cool during summers and warm during winters.Please Note: Image is for illustration purpose only.When buying a bedsheet you should check for TC or thread count which refers to the number of threads that make up one square inch of fabric. Typically, the finer the threads that can be woven together, the softer the fabric. The Solimo premium range of double bedsheets with 144 TC are soft, comfortable and suitable for all seasons. Each Solimo bedsheet is crafted to be light-weight and easy to wash at home.Solimo printed double bedsheets come in a large size: 90 inch x 100 inch or 228 cm x 254 cm, for making it easy to tuck-in below the bed. It is ideal for use on double beds with size 5 ft x 6.25 ft or smaller.You can use Solimo bedsheets all through the year. With a wide range of colours, designs and patterns, we help you create a unique look for your home. You can choose from amongst different designs such as floral, abstract and geometric to find a set that best suits your tastes and existing home decor.Welcome to the world of Solimo - a place where premium quality and great value go hand in hand. Every Solimo product is carefully built to deliver exceptional quality. Right from the materials used, to detailed quality checks, to thoughtful improvements, quality is at the core of everything we do. We invest our resources only on what is important to you and minimize costs on things like packaging, advertising and other extras that don’t add value. This helps us keep our costs low and create products that deliver more value for the price you pay. Expect a little more every time you buy a Solimo product.

aplus_text: The Solimo premium 144 TC bedsheet range is made from 100% cotton. This  double bedsheet is made from cotton that has been combed to retain only  long cotton fibers. This process makes the yarn strong and soft making  the bedsheet long lasting and soft to touch. Typically, the finer the threads that can be woven together, the softer the fabric. The Solimo premium range of double bedsheets with 144 TC are soft, comfortable and suitable for all seasons. Each Solimo bedsheet is crafted to be light-weight and easy to wash at home.Solimo printed double bedsheets come in a large size: 90 inch x 100 inch or 228 cm x 254 cm, for making it easy to tuck-in below the bed. It is ideal for use on double beds with size 5 ft x 6.25 ft or smaller.You can use Solimo bedsheets all through the year. With a wide range of colours, designs and patterns, we help you create a unique look for your home. You can choose from amongst different designs such as floral, abstract and geometric to find a set that best suits your tastes and existing home decor.Welcome to the world of Solimo - a place where premium quality and great value go hand in hand. Right from the materials used, to detailed quality checks, to thoughtful improvements, quality is at the core of everything we do. We invest our resources only on what is important to you and minimize costs on things like packaging, advertising and other extras that don’t add value. Their looped cloth design effectively absorbs water, so your guests will never need more than one towel to dry them off, from head to toe.Our towel set is an OEKO-TEX certified skin friendly product, which is an independent certification system that ensures textiles meet high safety and environmental standards.Trident's patent technology – AIR RICH yarn is a cotton yarn that has numerous tiny air pockets which provide better breath-ability to the fabric and helps in moisture management. aplus_text: Enhance your everyday afterbath experience with Trident’s advanced zero-twist FINESSE towels. These towels offer a velvety feel, greater bulk, lower lint, and enhanced performance. The ultrafine cotton used to create these towels brings you extra luxurious loftiness. When you upgrade to our Finesse towels, you'll enjoy greater plushness. These premium towels are perfect whether you have sensitive skin or you’re looking for the best towel for your guests. From the first laundering, you'll enjoy premium, deluxe plushness that only gets softer as time passes by.As our towels use longer cotton fibers that are inherently stronger because of the cotton species used, they last longer. The towels don’t shed and therefore retain more of their cotton over time.Cotton is a breathable material. The fibers allow air to pass through. It does not irritate the skin. So the towel won’t be itchy, making it soft and skin-friendly.The high-quality cotton fibers of these premium Luxurious towels have a tight weave that is innately durable. You won't have to worry about stretching or warping under regular use.With its velvety feel, Finesse is super soft and smooth. Made from our advanced Zero Twist technology, these towels have very low lint and thus they last longer than other towels.These Zero-Twist towels are inherently softer than regular towels. Their smooth loops touch your skin rather than twisted strands.Zero-twist towels use longer and stronger cotton fibers, allowing them to be looped through the towel base instead of twisting out from the towel.This means that you feel smooth loops when drying off rather than short stubby twists.We do follow a fine quality-making process which gives us 100% confidence in our product along with an independent system that ensures textiles meet high safety standards.

description: Fancy Fork Set to Eat Your Fruits: Birdie fruit fork set is a brightly coloured stand shaped like a tree with branches, which has six slots for the forks to be placed in. Good Decorative Piece for Your Table: The birdie fruit set is not only functional but also visually appealing. It is designed to look like a tree with birds perched on it. When you are not using it, this set makes for a beautiful table top. The colours are eye-catchy and render your table a cutesy charm. Made from 100% Food Grade Plastic: When it comes to plastic items, one is always worried about the quality and how it may affect our health. With the birdie fruit fork you can put these fears to rest. It is made of 100% food grade plastic which is recyclable. It is easy to clean and stack in the stand as well. Considering all this, birdie fruit fork set is a very useful purchase.

Typically, the finer the threads that can be woven together,  the softer the fabric. The Solimo premium range of double bedsheets  with 144 TC are soft, comfortable and suitable for all seasons. Each  Solimo bedsheet is crafted to be light-weight and easy to wash at home.Solimo printed double bedsheets come in a large size: 90  inch x 100 inch or 228 cm x 254 cm, for making it easy to tuck-in below  the bed. With a  wide range of colours, designs and patterns, we help you create a unique  look for your home. aplus_text: The Solimo premium 144 TC bedsheet range is made from 100% cotton. This  double bedsheet is made from cotton that has been combed to retain only  long cotton fibers. This process makes the yarn strong and soft making  the bedsheet long lasting and soft to touch. Typically, the finer the threads that can be woven together, the softer the fabric. The Solimo premium range of double bedsheets with 144 TC are soft, comfortable and suitable for all seasons. Each Solimo bedsheet is crafted to be light-weight and easy to wash at home.Solimo printed double bedsheets come in a large size: 90 inch x 100 inch or 228 cm x 254 cm, for making it easy to tuck-in below the bed. It is ideal for use on double beds with size 5 ft x 6.25 ft or smaller.You can use Solimo bedsheets all through the year. With a wide range of colours, designs and patterns, we help you create a unique look for your home. You can choose from amongst different designs such as floral, abstract and geometric to find a set that best suits your tastes and existing home decor.Welcome to the world of Solimo - a place where premium quality and great value go hand in hand. Every Solimo product is carefully built to deliver exceptional quality. Right from the materials used, to detailed quality checks, to thoughtful improvements, quality is at the core of everything we do. We invest our resources only on what is important to you and minimize costs on things like packaging, advertising and other extras that don’t add value. This helps us keep our costs low and create products that deliver more value for the price you pay. Expect a little more every time you buy a Solimo product.

aplus_text: The Solimo premium 144 TC bedsheet range is made from 100% cotton. This  double bedsheet is made from cotton that has been combed to retain only  long cotton fibers. This process makes the yarn strong and soft making  the bedsheet long lasting and soft to touch. The cotton fibers drain  away moisture, making the bedsheet breathable and comfortable.This bedsheet is suitable for use all-year round because cotton as a  fabric keeps you cool during summers and warm during winters.Please Note: Image is for illustration purpose only.When buying a bedsheet you should check for TC or thread count which refers to the number of threads that make up one square inch of fabric. Typically, the finer the threads that can be woven together, the softer the fabric. The Solimo premium range of double bedsheets with 144 TC are soft, comfortable and suitable for all seasons. Each Solimo bedsheet is crafted to be light-weight and easy to wash at home.Solimo printed double bedsheets come in a large size: 90 inch x 100 inch or 228 cm x 254 cm, for making it easy to tuck-in below the bed. It is ideal for use on double beds with size 5 ft x 6.25 ft or smaller.You can use Solimo bedsheets all through the year. With a wide range of colours, designs and patterns, we help you create a unique look for your home. You can choose from amongst different designs such as floral, abstract and geometric to find a set that best suits your tastes and existing home decor.Welcome to the world of Solimo - a place where premium quality and great value go hand in hand. Every Solimo product is carefully built to deliver exceptional quality. Right from the materials used, to detailed quality checks, to thoughtful improvements, quality is at the core of everything we do. We invest our resources only on what is important to you and minimize costs on things like packaging, advertising and other extras that don’t add value. This helps us keep our costs low and create products that deliver more value for the price you pay. Expect a little more every time you buy a Solimo product.

, Large size to make it easy to tuck-in below the bed  
, Long-lasting and luxuriously soft 144 TC bedsheet  
, Colour fade resistant for all-season use  
, Light weight and easy to wash at home  
, Size: Bedsheet - 90 inch x 100 inch or 228 cm x 254 cm, Pillow Cover - 18 inch x 27 inch or 46 cm x 68 cm  
, Pack Contents - 1 double bedsheet with 2 pillow covers

aplus_text: The Solimo premium 144 TC bedsheet range is made from 100% cotton. This  double bedsheet is made from cotton that has been combed to retain only  long cotton fibers. This process makes the yarn strong and soft making  the bedsheet long lasting and soft to touch. The cotton fibers drain  away moisture, making the bedsheet breathable and comfortable.This bedsheet is suitable for use all-year round because cotton as a  fabric keeps you cool during summers and warm during winters.Please Note: Image is for illustration purpose only.When buying a bedsheet you should check for TC or thread count which refers to the number of threads that make up one square inch of fabric. Typically, the finer the threads that can be woven together, the softer the fabric. The Solimo premium range of single bedsheets with 144 TC are soft, comfortable and suitable for all seasons. Each Solimo bedsheet is crafted to be light-weight and easy to wash at home.Solimo printed single bedsheets come in a large size: 60 inch x 90 inch or 152 cm x 228 cm, for making it easy to tuck-in below the bed. It is ideal for use on single beds with size 3 ft x 6.25 ft or smaller.You can use Solimo bedsheets all through the year. With a wide range of colours, designs and patterns, we help you create a unique look for your home. You can choose from amongst different designs such as floral, abstract and geometric to find a set that best suits your tastes and existing home decor.Welcome to the world of Solimo - a place where premium quality and great value go hand in hand. Every Solimo product is carefully built to deliver exceptional quality. Right from the materials used, to detailed quality checks, to thoughtful improvements, quality is at the core of everything we do. We invest our resources only on what is important to you and minimize costs on things like packaging, advertising and other extras that don’t add value. This helps us keep our costs low and create products that deliver more value for the price you pay. Expect a little more every time you buy a Solimo product.
